{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/fujiko-f-fujio-ayah-doraemon/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Fujiko F Fujio, Ayah Doraemon","content":"<p><em>Bro sis, kenal sama Fujiko F Fujio nggak?</em></p>\n<p><em>Dikasih clue deh&#8230;Aku ingin begini, aku ingin begitu. Ingin ini, ingin itu, banyak sekali…</em></p>\n<p>Buat yang masih kejamanan, pasti tahu kalo kalimat itu adalah penggalan lagu Doraemon. Nah, siapa sih orang di balik Doraemon yang tersohor di seluruh dunia itu? Dia adalah Fujitomo Hiroshi, atau yang kerap dikenal dengan Fujiko F. Fujio. Mangaka Jepang ini sudah berkecimpung di dunia manga sejak tahun ’50-an.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_91\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-91\" data-attachment-id=\"91\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/fujiko-f-fujio-ayah-doraemon/attachment/4-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/4-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"4\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/4-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/4-1.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-91 size-full\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/4-1.jpg\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/4-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/4-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-91\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Fujimoto Hiroshi (alabn.com)</p></div>\n<p>Nah, gimana sih cerita lahirnya Doraemon?</p>\n<p>Manga Doraemon lahir pada Desember 1969 lewat 6 majalah lokal, yaitu Yoiko (Anak Baik), Yochien (taman kanak-kanak), Shogaku Ichinensei (kelas 1 SD), dan Shogaku Yonnensei (kelas 4 SD). Kemudian sejak 1973, di majalah Shogaku Gogensei (kelas 5 SD) dan Shogaku Rokunensei (kelas 6 SD). Jangan kaget, cerita di setiap majalah itu berbeda. Jadi bisa dibayangkan, setiap kali terbit Fujiko F. Fujio harus mempersiapkan enam cerita berbeda.</p>\n<p>Doraemon menceritakan tentang anak pemalas bernama Nobi Nobita yang didatangi oleh robot kucing bernama Doraemon yang datang dari abad ke-22. Kantong Doraemon bisa mengeluarkan benda-benda ajaib untuk membantu Nobita. Majalah Doraemon disukai anak-anak. Maka di tahun 1970, muncul ide untuk membuat Doraemon dalam bentuk animasi kartun. Versi animasi yang dibuat, membuat Doraemon semakin dikenal dan mendunia.</p>\n<p>Di tahun ke-17 tepatnya pada tahun 1990, Doraemon masuk pasaran Indonesia. Doraemon dikenal dalam versi komik, film, dan souvenir.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_92\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-92\" data-attachment-id=\"92\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/fujiko-f-fujio-ayah-doraemon/attachment/5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"5\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/5.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-92 size-full\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/5.jpg\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-92\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Chapter pertama komik Doraemon (wikipedia.com)</p></div>\n<p>Selain Doraemon, Fujiko F. Fujio telah membuat 26 komik/ manga. Salah satunya Perman, di Indonesia serial animenya berjudul P-Man. Sosok berbakat ini terus mendedikasikan diri untuk berkarya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_93\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-93\" data-attachment-id=\"93\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/fujiko-f-fujio-ayah-doraemon/attachment/2-3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/2-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/2-2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/2-2.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-93 size-full\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/2-2.jpg\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/2-2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/2-2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-93\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Doraemon dan Perman (P-Man) (doraemon.wikia.com)</p></div>\n<p>Sang Pencipta lah yang berencana. Fujiko meninggal pada 1996 karena penyakit kanker. Meski begitu, karya-karyanya masih tetap hidup hingga sekarang. Dan sebagai penghargaan, Museum Doraemon atau Museum Fujiko telah resmi dibuka sejak 3 September 2011 di Kawasaki, Jepang.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_134\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-134\" data-attachment-id=\"134\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/fujiko-f-fujio-ayah-doraemon/attachment/3-6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/3-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"3\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/3-5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/3-5.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-134 size-full\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/3-5.jpg\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/3-5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/3-5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-134\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Selamat jalan Fujiko F. Fujio (Akibanation.com)</p></div>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"594b72dd-10a3-5773-a481-67a32c73797f"}}}